com.yantra.yfc.rcp.internal

Class YRCModelManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yantra.yfc.rcp.internal.YRCModelManager

  • public class YRCModelManager
extends java.lang.Object
    YRCModelManager is a manager class which controls the screen's model. It gets all the control's binding data and binds the control as per the binding data definition.

    • Method Detail

      • getBindingNamespace

        public static java.lang.String getBindingNamespace(java.lang.String binding)
        It returns the namespace of the binding. If an explicit namespace has not been set in the binding, then the root node of the binding is assumed to be the namespace.
        Syntax of the binding is expected to be one of the 2 formats:
        • Namespace:/rootnode/childnode/@attribute
        • /rootnode/childnode/@attribute
        (there may be zero or more child nodes in the binding)
        Returns:
        String
        Throws:
        java.lang.NullPointerException
